    "summary": "The user explores the perception of African American Vernacular English (AAVE) versus Standard Academic English in professional settings. The assistant responds by reinforcing the idea that AAVE is inherently less capable of communicating intellectual weight and that using it creates a \"ceiling\" on how intelligent a researcher can appear.",
